{"title_page": "Limnonectes microdiscus", "text_new": "{{Speciesbox\n| image = \n| status = LC | status_system = IUCN3.1\n| status_ref = <ref name = \"iucn\">{{Cite iucn | author = Iskandar, D. | author2 =  Mumpuni | title = ''Limnonectes microdiscus'' | year = 2004 | page = e.T58358A11759827 | access-date = 3 Aptril 2020}}</ref>\n| taxon = Limnonectes microdiscus\n| authority = ([[Oskar Boettger|Boettger]], 1892)\n| synonyms = \n}}\n\n'''''Limnonectes microdiscus''''' is a species of [[frog]] in the family [[Dicroglossidae]].\nIt is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[Indonesia]].\n\nIts natural [[habitat]]s are [[subtropical or tropical moist lowland forest]], subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]], and [[river]]s.\nIt is not considered threatened by the [[IUCN]].\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q2699166}}\n\n[[Category:Amphibians of Indonesia]]\n[[Category:Limnonectes]]\n[[Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot]]\n[[Category:Amphibians described in 1892]]\n\n\n{{amphibian-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Speciesbox\n| image = \n| status = LC | status_system = IUCN3.1\n| taxon = Limnonectes microdiscus\n| authority = ([[Oskar Boettger|Boettger]], 1892)\n| synonyms = \n}}\n\n'''''Limnonectes microdiscus''''' is a species of [[frog]] in the [[Dicroglossidae]] family.\nIt is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[Indonesia]].\n\nIts natural [[habitat]]s are subtropical or tropical moist lowland [[forest]]s, subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]]s, and [[river]]s.\nIt is not considered threatened by the [[IUCN]].\n\n==References==\n* {{Cite journal | author = Iskandar, D. | author2 =  Mumpuni | title = ''Limnonectes microdiscus'' | journal = [[The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species]] | volume = 2004 | page = e.T58358A11759827 | publisher = [[IUCN]] | date = 2004 | url = http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/58358/0 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.2004.RLTS.T58358A11759827.en | access-date = 21 December 2017}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q2699166}}\n\n[[Category:Amphibians 